welcome_message_body: "Welcome to charming Oberhaching, known for its scenic beauty and warm hospitality. We invite you to explore and enjoy all that our city has to offer. Have a wonderful stay!"

terminals.description: The main terminal at Oberpfaffenhofen Airport, serving domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Terminal 1
terminals.description: The largest and oldest terminal at Franz Josef Strauss Airport, serving mainly Lufthansa and Star Alliance airlines.

terminals.name: Terminal 2
terminals.description: The newer terminal at Franz Josef Strauss Airport, serving mainly non-Star Alliance airlines.

terminals.name: Terminal 3
